548
00:32:31,560 --> 00:32:32,960
Bukan kah kamu lelaki?

549
00:32:32,960 --> 00:32:34,600
Kenapa anda ragu-ragu?

550
00:32:35,200 --> 00:32:36,520
Kami kekurangan seorang pemain.

551
00:32:40,400 --> 00:32:41,400
Saya akan bergabung dengan Yiyi.

552
00:32:41,880 --> 00:32:42,600
Saya tidak setuju.

553
00:32:42,680 --> 00:32:43,480
Lalu siapa yang kamu inginkan?

554
00:32:43,480 --> 00:32:44,960
Saya akan bergabung dengan lelaki ini.

555
00:32:45,200 --> 00:32:46,440
Tidakkah kamu bilang dia sangat baik?

556
00:32:46,720 --> 00:32:47,240
Wow.

557
00:32:47,440 --> 00:32:48,680
Tapi bagaimana jika kamu kalah?

558
00:32:48,880 --> 00:32:50,040
Apakah saya pernah kalah?

559
00:32:50,120 --> 00:32:51,000
Baiklah.

560
00:32:51,280 --> 00:32:51,880
Long Qi.

561
00:32:52,560 --> 00:32:53,400
Anda menang.

562
00:32:53,840 --> 00:32:54,680
Dia milikmu.

563
00:32:54,800 --> 00:32:56,280
